text: Khristo Kachev (born 17 December 1953) is a Bulgarian equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Bulgaria Category:Equestrians at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
